nodes.text: A city located on the planet Jabiim was destroyed by a Force storm generated by the Sith Lord Fulminiss sometime between 3681 BBY and 3640 BBY. Fulminiss's actions were in response to the local Jabiimi's resistance to the Sith Empire's rule of their world.
The city and its destruction were first mentioned in the Codex entry for Fulminiss within Star Wars: The Old Republic, a video game released by BioWare and LucasArts in 2011.
